380
00:37:19,278 --> 00:37:21,322
I wouldn't say we were close…

381
00:37:25,159 --> 00:37:27,078
But I guess so.

382
00:37:27,161 --> 00:37:28,412
Usually,

383
00:37:29,080 --> 00:37:32,875
