about what happened to Henry's mom…

388
00:38:06,450 --> 00:38:07,952
Never mind.

389
00:38:08,035 --> 00:38:11,247
I have no intentions
of getting involved with her anymore.

390
00:38:24,051 --> 00:38:25,261
Come in.

391
00:38:27,388 --> 00:38:29,098
