401
00:39:09,513 --> 00:39:11,432
and work together.

402
00:39:12,767 --> 00:39:14,352
Don't be nervous.

403
00:39:23,861 --> 00:39:26,989
Relax your body.

404
00:39:31,285 --> 00:39:34,789
Let's focus all our energy on our hearts.

405
00:39:37,333 --> 00:39:39,543
All right, let's all close our eyes.

406
00:39:44,006 --> 00:39:46,300
Focus on the center of your heart.

407
00:39:49,053 --> 00:39:50,596
Try and imagine

408
00:39:51,806 --> 00:39:54,725
that you've taken out your heart
and placed it in your hand.

409
00:40:10,658 --> 00:40:12,451
-Gosh, Eun-pyo!
-Goodness!

410
00:40:12,535 --> 00:40:13,953
-Somebody call 911!
-Goodness!

411
00:40:14,036 --> 00:40:15,955
-Somebody call 911!
